subSection.paragraph:
The methanolic extract of 

P. igniarius

was subjected to column chromatography over MCI CHP20P, silica gel, Sephadex LH-20, ODS, and high performance liquid chromatography purification to yield seven undescribed 22-hydroxylanostane triterpenoids, phellinols A-G (
1–7
), together with three known sterols (
8–10
) (
Fig. 1
). The known compounds were identified as ergosta-7,22-diene-3 
β
-ol (
8
) (
Ziegenbein et al., 2006
), ergosta-7,22-diene-3- one (
9
) (
Liu et al., 2009
), and phellinignincisterol C (
10
) (
Wu et al., 2010
), by comparison of their spectroscopic data with those reported in literatures.
